<div class="noinclude"><span class="script">template.XULRefElem()</span></div>
<p>Defines the columns of a <span class="script">template.XULElem("grid")</span>. Child <span class="script">template.XULElem("column")</span> elements define the individual columns to appear in the grid. The <code>columns</code> element may be nested inside another <code>columns</code> element. Other elements placed inside a <code>columns</code> element occupy the full height of the grid and are placed in their corresponding positions between the columns.</p>
